The paper deals with a combinatorial optimization problem in which the authors propose a local search heuristic to obtain a constant factor approximation. This suggests that the paper could belong to the categories of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), operations research (cs.OR), computational complexity (cs.CC), or machine learning (cs.LG). However, since the problem involves capacitated facilities and medians, it is more likely to belong to the categories of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) or operations research (cs.OR).
